about.title: LLP Yangiyer Flour Trading is an independent, family owned company. Operating since 1991. Based in the heart of central Asia. LLP Yangiyer Flour Trading operates from their purpose built for producing best quality wheat flour from first class flour to second and third class and offering a service second to none at very competitive prices. With over 30 years’ experience in the wholesale and production market industry. our staff will use their experience and knowledge to help customers achieve their fresh produce collections or deliveries on a daily basis.
